    Hi Hiral,<br>
    <br>
    You have to add "OMPI_IMPORTS" as a preprocessor definition in you
    project configuration. Or a easier way is to use the mpicc command
    line.<br>
    <br>
    Please also take a look into the output of "mpicc --showme", it will
    give you the complete compile options.<br>
    <br>
    <br>
    Regards,<br>
    Shiqing<br>
    <br>
