                                                Hiral,
                                                <div>&nbsp;</div>
                                                <div>1.3.4 is quite old,
                                                  please use the latest
                                                  version. As Damien
                                                  noted, the full
                                                  fortran support is in
                                                  1.5 series, it's only
                                                  experimental in 1.4
                                                  series. And there is
                                                  only F77 bingdings on
                                                  Windows, no F90
                                                  bindings. Another
                                                  choice is to use the
                                                  released binary
                                                  installers to avoid
                                                  compiling everything
                                                  by yourself.</div>
